$interpreted: Kittyeyes: We've finally arrived in Atlas...
Koll: Arwoo~?
Kittyeyes: Roger's condition is getting worse by the day; probably something to do with that damn monster bite he suffered.
Kittyeyes: Aosta said if we obtain a blood sample from the same type of monster, he can help us.
Koll: Wooo~?
Kittyeyes: No worries. I've heard Jeff describe the features of that monster a million times already. I won't miss it.
Kittyeyes: I know it's very risky, but this is the only way to save Roger.
Kittyeyes: You're so annoying! If you don't want to save our brother then I'll go by myself. Stop following me!
Kittyeyes: God, why is it so creepy around here? Better hurry and find the Dragoneye Lake where the mines were at...
Kittyeyes: What the heck is this!?
Kittyeyes: Huff~ Puff~ that was really scary...
Kittyeyes: There's more!?
Kittyeyes: Koll!
Koll: Arooooo~~
Kittyeyes: Ok, let's do this, together!
Kittyeyes: UGH, so irritating. How come there's still more...
Kittyeyes: Hmm, is that?
Kittyeyes: Matches all the features Jeff described...
Kittyeyes: That's the one. Koll, let's get it!
Kittyeyes: What are you doing, the monster that infected bro Roger is right there! Let go of me. I said let go of me, now!
Roger: Are you stupid? What are you thinking going to such a dangerous place? If not for Koll, you would've been long dead!
Kittyeyes: B-Because Aosta...he said he could cure your disease, as long as...
Roger: So you believed his nonsense? What else did you tell him about me?
Kittyeyes: A-About how you often get headaches these days, how you get infuriated easily, and...
Roger: I avoid him precisely because I don't want him to know about my condition. Can't you tell that he's only interested in dissecting me for research?
Roger: Do you want him to swoop in and take advantage of me?
Kittyeyes: How would I know, I only wanted to help you out!
Roger: Whatever, you better take some time to reflect on what you've done and realize your mistakes!
Kittyeyes: ...Wanting to protect the person you like, is that a mistake too?
